The complete list of winners for Homecoming  was announced this week PERIOD

Alpha Kappa Lambda fraternity  Fraternity Row and Phi Mu sorority were awarded first place honors for the overall weekend competition homecoming chair Carrie Sarhangi said PERIOD Phi Delta Theta fraternity  N PERIOD Burrowes Road and Theta Alpha Pi sorority placed second and Delta Upsilon fraternity  Locust Lane and Pi Beta Phi sorority achieved third place honors PERIOD

In the banner competition first place honors were awarded to Sigma Nu fraternity  N PERIOD Burrowes Road in the white division and Zeta Beta Tau fraternity  E PERIOD Fairmount Ave PERIOD and Gamma Sigma Sigma sorority in the blue division PERIOD

The winners of the Nittany Pursuit scavenger hunt were Delta Upsilon and Pi Beta Phi in the blue division and the Lion Ambassadors in the white division PERIOD

Sigma Nus Harry Potterthemed float was voted the best of the white division in the float competition PERIOD Tau Epsilon Phi fraternity  E PERIOD Foster Ave. and the Society of Women Engineers had the best float in the blue division with Toy Story PERIOD
